{
  "stem": "24885.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So when they tell you the stories they didn't know about it-- it was a private company.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They knew what was going on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They used to bid on all the material to supply to the crematoriums.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hersh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My name in German Herschel, so it was Hersh.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We had a-- after two, three days working with him, you know, he was very honest.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He says, I'll make it for you very easy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You don't have to go to there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I can do it right here for you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I looked at him and I don't know if I had tears in my eyes or whatever, and I walked away.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't say anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But it was a very traumatic experience.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not that I didn't know by then-- I already knew what was happening.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But until it hits you yourself, you don't know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You don't know what's happening.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then I think I mentioned to you in 1940, they bought into our camp about 20 or 30 Russian prisoners of war.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And then one day, those guys decided to escape.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "One of them I think was Jacob, his first name, was Jewish, but he spoke German.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was an-- very-- it wasn't very common between the Russians to speak German.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But they were all-- he was a tank driver, he told me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they lost their battle at the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I helped him-- I got him some clothes, some suits and so on, whatever I could get together, because they wanted to escape in civilian clothes.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He didn't want me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I would have gone with him had he asked me, but he didn't want me.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
